Compilation:
- In A1 directory, run 'premake4 gmake'
- In A1 directory, run 'make'
- In A1 directory, run './A1'

Manual:
- Finish all feature. Add two files 'Avatar.cpp' and 'Avatar.hpp' for Avatar class.
- Assume each time sphere will move 1 step with length 1.
- For persistent, release after clicking and dragging the left button of mouse will let the maze keep rotating. 
If click the mouse button again, it will stop rotating.
